<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Vendor Application Update</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #2E7D32; padding: 40px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #FDC500; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .header p { color: #ffffff; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; }
    .body { padding: 40px 32px; }
    .body h2 { color: #151515; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 8px; }
    .body p { color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .reason-box { background-color: #fff3f3; border-left: 4px solid #e53935; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .reason-box p { color: #c62828; margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .next-steps { background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .next-steps h3 { color: #151515; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .step-num { background-color: #2E7D32; color: white; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-text { color: #555555; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding-top: 2px; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 24px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #9b9b9b; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Shopa</h1>
      <p>Vendor Application Update</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Your vendor application was not approved</h2>
      <p>Thank you for applying to become a vendor on Shopa. Unfortunately, your application for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> was not approved at this time.</p>
      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box">
        <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3>What you can do next:</h3>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-text">Review the reason provided above carefully</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-text">Ensure your student ID is clear and valid</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-text">Re-apply with the correct information</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>If you believe this decision was made in error, please contact your campus administrator.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Shopa. All rights reserved.<br/>Crawford University Campus Marketplace</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
